theorem toListModel_expandIfNecessary [BEq α] [Hashable α] [PartialEquivBEq α] (m : Raw₀ α β) :
    Perm (toListModel (expandIfNecessary m).1.2) (toListModel m.1.2) := by
  rw [expandIfNecessary]
  dsimp
  split
  · exact Perm.refl _
  · dsimp
    exact toListModel_expand
